quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  42,23,"Ako niko ka omwikhoyo ka Nyasaye aboolera Abasumba bebe basuubila mana nibakhola amalayi. Boola mbu: “Esie shebarebanga omurungo kwosikwosi tawe halali obuheli khubeekho.” Ne ukhola lilayi, khumumetela lilayi. Toto Nyasaye nomulesheli, wokhukalusia orio ikhongo muno."
  42,24,"Nohomba baboolanga mbu: “Achishilinjia Nyasaye amakhuwa kobubeyi kabulaho.” Ne Nyasaye niyenya, naasuba khumwoyo kwo. Ne Nyasaye yosinjia obukori, ne atinyisia obwatoto khumakhuwa keke. Toto ye ni Omumanyi muno khukali mubilifu."
  42,25,"Naye niye ufuchililanga okhusaba eshileshelo khwa Abasumba be, ne aleshelanga tsimbi, ne yamanya muno akamukholanga."
  42,26,"Ne niye ufuchililanga balia basuubila mana nibakhola amalayi, ne abametalanga emikabo chichie, ne abakhayi bali neshinyasio eshilulu."
  42,27,"Ne Nyasaye ahelesinjia Abasumba bebe omukabo omunji, bakhakholile obufuru khushialo. Halali yeshinjia khushichelo shiayenya. Toto ye yamanya obulayi Abasumba bebe, ne abalolanga."
  42,28,"Naye niye wishinjia ifula abandu nibawesiyekhwo omwoyo muno. Ne aswaninjia tsimbabaasi tsitsie, naye niye omulindi watoto, witsomibungwa muno."
  42,29,"Ne mubimanyisio bibie nokhulongwa khwelikulu nende eshialo, nende tsisolo tsiayaswaniamwo, naye ali nobunyali muno bwokhubikhung’asia niyenya."
  42,30,"Ne amasila kosikosi kamunyoola, karulana nende kemikhono chienyu chikholele, ne aleshelanga amanji."
  42,31,"Ne enywe shimwakhashila khushialo tawe, ne mubula omulindi nohomba ubakhonya ulali Nyasaye tawe."